channel.title: Gui problem
channel.description:
A few errors have come from the client I am using for my server. I have overcome most of them but have not managed a fix for this particular error. Only one of my players has this error and it's on one of his two PCs. [URL=http://img816.imageshack.us/i/errorrj.png/][IMG]http://img816.imageshack.us/img816/7839/errorrj.png[/img][/URL] I've had a Jframe error like that before for me and another player which I fixed with this run text
[code]@echo off title Armadyl Pkz Client java -Xmx300m -cp . Jframe 10 0 highmem members 32 pause[/code] Anyone know what I should do to fix this error?
